  <name>VescTool</name>
  <summary>VESC® Tool is the all new and 100% revised replacement for BLDC-Tool</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
    VESC Tool can be used with the latest VESC compatible Hardware and most VESC based Hardware of the past. It does not only allow you to configure your VESCs and upload the latest firmware – it allows you to generate real time data and find out how to set up your drive with perfection. VESC® Tool has tons of features but you won't get lost. Wizards will guide you and every setting has a help button that shows explanations for easy understanding.
    </p>
  </description>

